  1413вҶ’//! \fn int CreateAMRMPITag(int lid, int ox1, int ox2, int ox3)
  1414вҶ’//  \brief calculate an MPI tag for AMR block transfer
  1415вҶ’// tag = local id of destination (remaining bits) + ox1(1 bit) + ox2(1 bit) + ox3(1 bit)
  1416вҶ’//       + physics(5 bits)
  1417вҶ’
